<subSubSection id="C3234CA1FFE7FF8345E7F8EBFA848730" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B861F2AFFE7FF8345E7F8EBFA848730" blockId="3.[151,1437,1084,1902]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">
<emphasis id="B94DC338FFE7FF8345E7F8EBFE858778" bold="true" box="[199,308,1804,1830]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C3964A9FFE7FF834464F8EAFDB28778" authority="Viraktamath &amp; Yeshwanth, 2021" authorityName="Viraktamath &amp; Yeshwanth" authorityYear="2021" box="[324,515,1804,1830]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dalhousiensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B94DC338FFE7FF834464F8EAFDB28778" box="[324,515,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. dalhousiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B94DC338FFE7FF83472DF8EBFDD98778" bold="true" box="[525,616,1804,1830]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A27E7E43FFE7FF83472DF8EBFDD98778" box="[525,616,1804,1830]" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
externally resembles 
<taxonomicName id="4C3964A9FFE7FF834643F8EAFC5E8778" authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" box="[867,1007,1804,1830]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ganeshai">
<emphasis id="B94DC338FFE7FF834643F8EAFC5E8778" box="[867,1007,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. ganeshai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis id="B94DC338FFE7FF83410AF8EAFB7B8778" box="[1066,1226,1804,1830]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">
<taxonomicName id="4C3964A9FFE7FF83410AF8EAFB778778" authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" box="[1066,1222,1804,1830]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vagdeviae">M. vagdeviae</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
It differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C3964A9FFE7FF83405EF8EAFF4D8714" authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ganeshai">
<emphasis id="B94DC338FFE7FF83405EF8EAFF4D8714" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. ganeshai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the aedeagal shaft being narrowed apically compared to slightly broadened in lateral view beyond the dorsal curvature in the latter; from 
<taxonomicName id="4C3964A9FFE7FF83473FF8B2FD078730" authorityName="Viraktamath" authorityYear="1996" box="[543,694,1876,1902]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vagdeviae">
<emphasis id="B94DC338FFE7FF83473FF8B2FD078730" box="[543,694,1876,1902]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="356">M. vagdeviae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
it differs in having much longer pygofer ventral process.
</paragraph>
